Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的特別熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但出了這麼多汗應該會變瘦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑拿服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會出汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒法好好彈奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  來玩聯想遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到日本的夏天會想到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO  NO  NO  NO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是中華涼麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說唯怎麼盡想到吃的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那·就·是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪談！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是流傳在這個學校的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個學生為了拿忘記的東西  晚上來到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從應該沒人的音樂教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了鋼琴的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:06:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於好奇偷看了一下音樂教室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小佐和正在特訓一個要考音大的學生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就沒有變得涼快的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過焦躁對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣越是拼命扇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來的時候就越是熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你們想著「好熱好熱」  才會變得更熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的心態問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小律  我們來想點涼快的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼快的事情嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍打～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快啊  小律～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心態問題啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輸  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想著「好涼快」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快  好涼快  好涼快  好涼快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快  好涼快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱  果然無法想像涼快的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  之前整理的時候好像把電風扇放進儲物室了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在這裡大家就都能吹到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全吹不到風！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在最後面  所以沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  律
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼  以最大功率按下開關！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～涼～快～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（謝謝  我們永遠不會忘記你的  輕音社全員）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經毫無辦法了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我帶了冰塊來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是想做刨冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我忘了帶刨冰機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼涼的好舒服～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來  我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…好像不涼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天熱  所以冰融化得快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  你去拿冰來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  唯你去拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太熱了  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是冬天的暖爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小律去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛  腰痛的舊病發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾啊  明明是我先進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡腳的時間是我比較短
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這冰扔掉太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼放到小豬的水缸裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自動調節溫度的裝置在  小豬沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的啦  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐的玩笑一點都不像玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  它的成長好像和水缸大小有關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓它長大就一定要換個大點的水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  蛻皮也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豬也想要成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我家有多餘的大水缸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要怎麼搬過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老師不是有車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜託老師看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  最近小佐和都沒有來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不很好嗎  她在的話不就更熱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計她是被這天氣擊倒在哪個角落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒資格笑別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來辦公室有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什麼  要帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  看一下小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  它在水裡不是很舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蛻皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們想把紬家的大水缸換過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用老師的車子搬一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  給你浮冰果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上去搬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真容易對付…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去啦  好歹是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  光是小律去太不公平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去  想坐坐小佐和的車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵不要偷跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我不能去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是去紬家裡  總之先讓紬上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那紬紬去坐副駕駛席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和梓喵加小律還有小澪一起坐後面就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這車限坐四人  只剩兩個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小律代替小佐和上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰來開車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車能大點多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是為了你們買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  水缸挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好車上光裝水缸就很勉強了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那水缸放後座  能去的就只有紬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了老師的車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請問  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:13:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安符  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的座位看的好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個能動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  果然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會再去家庭訪問的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豬  久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  大水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過邊上曬到太陽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  遮一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有膠帶沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得儲物間應該有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就回辦公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事情只能拜託小佐和的說～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…我還是回去算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·不·幹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  要不要嘗嘗巧克力刨冰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空調啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們自己買空調好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪來那麼多錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工啦～打工～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…學姐你們不準備升學考試了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去問問學生會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家會不會聽我們的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價錢在那兒擺著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…果然還是需要賄賂一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  和和說過她想要台電腦來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  紬！去準備一台電腦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有買電腦的錢不就能買空調了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  和！唯中暑暈倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死前只想…打響一次響…指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的是金空調  還是銀空調？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊  我想要的只是普通的空調
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在太誠實了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把這新空調送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這算哪出三分錢戲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（三分錢戲劇：由《三分錢歌劇》（Die Dreigroschenoper）\N衍生而來的名詞，現指演技糟糕的戲劇）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉吵到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是有事來拜託和和…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間…好涼快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間裡有空調啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂用職權！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…虧我那麼信任你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子社長會議上不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校會給活動室加裝空調
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有需要的社團請提交申請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記交申請了…啊痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在還來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之在明天的社長會議上提交申請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會議？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會議？開什麼會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒參加過  不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副了不起的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會議有不隨人所願的結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？空調一定得要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能認真去申請了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們先來練習一下會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想會有什麼反對意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後準備好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那麼有議題的同學請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  輕音社希望加裝空調！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成現在田井中同學意見的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員贊成就沒意義了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反對的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  之前會議上就提過空調的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖到現在再講實在太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  感覺輕音社沒怎麼練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的需要空調嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！我不要空調了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怎麼行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要有些反駁才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事！小律一定做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是社長  姐姐  還是鼓手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不練習的輕音社不需要空調
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有在練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密特訓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要秘密進行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  我認為社團活動不是只有練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  唯難得說了點正經話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增進友情  促進學年交流…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有吃蛋糕啊  去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  輕音社果然用不著空調吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空調我們就練習！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命演奏的話會出很多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲鼓是體力活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有空調的話  夏天很難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有空調的話我們的演奏會更酷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  這樣到時候就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊衝啊  小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們見識一下社長的真正實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  有其它議題的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請為輕音社購買空調
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人反對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是OK…了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是會長  學生會今年的預算已經很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換學生會影印機的事  放到明年也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對啊  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能好好練習了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先休息吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始咯
